{"tid":2490844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國2021 Q1 GDP年增長18.3%","createTime":"2021-04-16T02:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T02:52:40.000Z","uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"976d21680f6166bdf0ee86b344320a8135bf0740","tid":2490844,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:10:44.000Z","msg":"在去年新冠疫情影響的低基數下，中國今年第一季GDP按年增長18.3%，略不及預期的18.5%。<br />\n<br />\n國家統計局周五（16日）公布數據表示，首季國民經濟開局良好，國內生產總值按年增長18.3%，受到上年較低基數、員工就地過年工作日有所增加等不可比因素影響；另一方面，首季度環比增長0.6%，兩年平均增長5%，表明中國經濟穩定恢復。"},{"pid":"41df90f2e3d38c3120e6d1f5f11d0090c481a9b9","tid":2490844,"uid":59037,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:22:32.000Z","msg":"大陸統計數據幾時可信過，BBC先前已經質疑做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7997410109d323e2e698d15c5f2ef7237f42ed","tid":2490844,"uid":202383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:23:32.000Z","msg":"同比無意義 上年Q1可以ignore"},{"pid":"c8806d43dba234f0c7f48a5afe606856ebea2c68","tid":2490844,"uid":104489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:25:50.000Z","msg":"同上一季比得 0.6%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通漲都唔只啦"},{"pid":"917545bf916b8460c08880fd46369bd79b907435","tid":2490844,"uid":287269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41df90f2e3d38c3120e6d1f5f11d0090c481a9b9","tid":2490844,"uid":59037,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:22:32.000Z","msg":"大陸統計數據幾時可信過，BBC先前已經質疑做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"現任中共中央政治局常委、國務院副總理李克強，二○○七年三月擔任遼寧省委書記時，曾對當時的美國大使雷德表示，中國的國內生產毛額（ＧＤＰ）都是「人造的」，並不可靠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/focus/paper/450093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Ffocus%2Fpaper%2F450093&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwB0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3